    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Great news for savvy car shoppers \u2014 this vehicle is in genuinely good condition and ready to impress! It runs and drives smoothly, with solid mechanical health and a well-maintained interior that shows real pride of ownership. You'll notice some minor cosmetic wear here and there, as expected with a used vehicle, but nothing that takes away from its overall appeal or reliability. Whether you're upgrading your daily driver or looking for a dependable family car, this one delivers real value at an honest price!",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "I want to be upfront and honest with potential buyers: this vehicle is in poor condition and is priced accordingly. It has significant mechanical issues that will require attention \u2014 expect repairs to be necessary before relying on it for regular driving. The exterior shows considerable wear, including visible dents, scratches, and fading paint beyond normal cosmetic blemishes. The interior is worn with tears, staining, and signs of heavy use. This car may be suitable for someone mechanically inclined looking for a project vehicle, or for parts. It is not recommended as a primary daily driver without substantial investment in repairs. What you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and represents a solid, dependable used car option. The exterior shows only minor wear consistent with normal use \u2014 a few small scratches and light surface marks, but no significant dents or rust. The interior is clean and well-maintained, with upholstery that is intact and comfortable, functioning controls, and minimal wear on high-contact surfaces like the steering wheel and pedals. Mechanically, the car runs well \u2014 the engine starts reliably, transmission shifts smoothly, and all major systems including brakes, suspension, and cooling are in proper working order. Some age-related wear is present, as expected for a used vehicle, but nothing that detracts from everyday reliability. A pre-purchase inspection is welcome and encouraged. Sold as-is, but honestly priced to reflect what you're actually getting.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable project car or a budget-friendly beater to get you from A to B? This vehicle runs and drives, which is a genuine plus at this price point! It does show significant wear \u2014 expect cosmetic issues, some mechanical quirks, and the kind of character that comes with age and use. It's priced to reflect its current condition honestly, making it a great pick for a handy buyer or someone who just needs basic transportation without breaking the bank. Come take a look and see if it fits your needs!",
      "price": 6500.0,
